{"tid":687601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老婦藥房偷紙巾　職員報警拉人","createTime":"2018-06-02T11:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T12:41:07.000Z","uid":122,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d8be78f91b401e2887fd83710f5c0972c975a1a2","tid":687601,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"北角英皇道近電廠街一間藥房，下午1時，警方接獲女職員報案，指一名老婦偷取一包放在近門口紙箱內的紙巾，價值約33港元，於是立即將她截停。警方到場調查後，以涉嫌盜竊將老婦拘捕。據職員稱，有人月前曾到上址犯案，當日體諒她年邁未有報警，今次發現她再出現，遂提高警覺監視。"},{"pid":"ca6e22e786f60feae543c9ffff5d9f1b06cab6cd","tid":687601,"uid":185683,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db6fffdf3e67c6eb44d84828fe296e6476898c68","tid":687601,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"藥房特登找少錢可唔可以告偷竊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4337c672865cb3d18dcb8148de755e90acb55a88","tid":687601,"uid":135767,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c87b7ab52c32a71a57f5559b719ad0f20d01c3a9","tid":687601,"uid":46943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"捉鳩曬啲老野啦<br />\n成日博你平平地<br />\n俾人捉同情又有人幫手俾錢<br />\n話恰鳩老人家<br />\n但係年中偷唔少<br />\n變相恰鳩小商戶"},{"pid":"95be9be87dfc565c553d0c36af777b651a77d5e7","tid":687601,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"22c900a6b39b66d5a32f26e25bec397594fba0b2","tid":687601,"uid":50984,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"廢老:阿婆好窮冇錢開飯呀,好心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d658e210a68e73cdf481b065875aa228f916c95d","tid":687601,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c87b7ab52c32a71a57f5559b719ad0f20d01c3a9","tid":687601,"uid":46943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"